1.0.0.name: wordpress/outbrain
1.0.0.description:
Outbrain automatically places your best content at the footer of your article to guide readers towards other posts they may be interseted in. You have the option of text or thumbnails and can also obtain reader feedback with the use of our rating system. Our reporting system allows you to see what articles are getting the highest click throughs and track your most popular posts. Blogs with over 1,000,000 PVs have the opporunity to generate revenue. If you think your blog qualifies,email us at info@outbrain.com for more information.
The plugin is completely free and takes about 60 seconds to install.
